verbose_text: With the orally administrated 3,4-DHPEA-EDA, the late appearance of HVA (T max = 60 min), compared with HT (T max = 30 min) and HVAOH (T max = 30 min), supports the stepwise metabolism of 3,4-DHPEA-EDA, including 3,4-DHPEA-EDA-related polyphenols (bound form or unbound form), to HT, HVAOH, and HVA in this order.
